  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="KT97-kilavi">varaivu nīṭṭittavaḻit talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">Uttered to the confidante by HER when [he] delayed marriage.</p>
          </div>



        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="KT97">
<l>                yāṉē yīṇṭai yēṉē yeṉṉalaṉē</l>
<l>                yāṉā nōyoṭu kāṉa laḵtē</l>
<l>                tuṟaivaṉ ṟammū rāṉē</l>
<l>                maṟaiyala rāki maṉṟat taḵtē.</l>
             </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
            <l>I, I am here. My innocence</l>
            <l>with endless pain in the seashore grove.</l>
            <l>The man from the ghat
                <choice>
                    <seg>in his<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">tuṟaivaṉ</term> (sg.) + <term xml:lang="ta">tam</term> (pl.): how to understand this? He is not in their (i.e. his own people's) village (cf. 3b)?</note> village.</seg>
                    <seg>[is] in their village.</seg>
                </choice>
            </l>
            <l>The secret become gossip of public places.</l>

            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
